1090
00:42:42,090 --> 00:42:43,980
Don't apply any ointment or pharmaceutical product

1091
00:42:43,980 --> 00:42:45,710
to the wound without the doctor's advice.

1092
00:42:45,830 --> 00:42:47,510
Don't pop any blisters.

1093
00:42:47,510 --> 00:42:49,440
And don't blow on the abrasions

1094
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:50,700
to avoid contamination.

1095
00:42:50,700 --> 00:42:52,170
In case of emergency,

1096
00:42:52,380 --> 00:42:53,600
please send the patient to the hospital immediately.
